The Board shall waive the education requirement under § 14-5C-09(c)(3) of this subtitle if on or before September 30, 2013, an individual:
Has passed the national certifying examination by the Board of Registered Polysomnographic Technologists or another examination approved by the Board;
Is certified by the Board of Registered Polysomnographic Technologists as a registered polysomnographic technologist;
Has submitted an application for licensure to the Board; and
Meets all of the requirements under § 14-5C-09(b) and (c)(1) and (2) of this subtitle.
